            "event_card_title": "Music Quiz",
            "event_description": "<h3><strong>Music Quiz</strong></h3>\r\nGuess the song!\r\n\r\nStarting @ 20:30\r\n\r\nThe music quiz is an old favorite at Madame Claude.\r\n\r\nThe rules of the game: Once everyone is comfortable and settled in the main room, they’re divided into teams usually based on the table where they’re sitting. Next our lovely host plays songs and asks for either the name of the song or the artist.\r\n\r\nThe songs are absolutely random and could just as likely be an obscure song buried deep in David Bowie’s massive discography, or one of Tailor Swifts biggest hits.\r\n\r\nEach team has equal chance to shout out the answer to get the point.\r\n\r\nThe team with the most points wins a bottle of sekt! May the team with the best musical knowledge win!\r\n\r\n&nbsp;",
            "event_day_name": "Music Quiz"
        }
