            "event_description": "<div class=\"xjyslct xjbqb8w x972fbf xcfux6l x1qhh985 xm0m39n x9f619 x1rg5ohu xdj266r x11i5rnm xat24cr x1mh8g0r xexx8yu x4uap5 x18d9i69 xkhd6sd x1n2onr6 x16tdsg8 xh8yej3\">\r\n<div class=\"x78zum5 xdt5ytf xwib8y2 x1y1aw1k\">\r\n<div class=\"x9f619 x1n2onr6 x1ja2u2z x78zum5 x2lah0s x1nhvcw1 x1cy8zhl xozqiw3 x1q0g3np x1pi30zi x1swvt13 xexx8yu xykv574 xbmpl8g x4cne27 xifccgj\">\r\n<div class=\"x9f619 x1n2onr6 x1ja2u2z x78zum5 xdt5ytf x193iq5w xeuugli x1r8uery x1iyjqo2 xs83m0k xamitd3 xsyo7zv x16hj40l x10b6aqq x1yrsyyn\">\r\n<div class=\"x78zum5 xdt5ytf xz62fqu x16ldp7u\">\r\n<div class=\"xu06os2 x1ok221b\">\r\n<div class=\"xjyslct xjbqb8w x972fbf xcfux6l x1qhh985 xm0m39n x9f619 x1rg5ohu xdj266r x11i5rnm xat24cr x1mh8g0r xexx8yu x4uap5 x18d9i69 xkhd6sd x1n2onr6 x16tdsg8 xh8yej3\">\r\n<div class=\"x78zum5 xdt5ytf xwib8y2 x1y1aw1k\">\r\n<div class=\"x9f619 x1n2onr6 x1ja2u2z x78zum5 x2lah0s x1nhvcw1 x1cy8zhl xozqiw3 x1q0g3np x1pi30zi x1swvt13 xexx8yu xykv574 xbmpl8g x4cne27 xifccgj\">\r\n<div class=\"x9f619 x1n2onr6 x1ja2u2z x78zum5 xdt5ytf x193iq5w xeuugli x1r8uery x1iyjqo2 xs83m0k xamitd3 xsyo7zv x16hj40l x10b6aqq x1yrsyyn\">\r\n<div class=\"x78zum5 xdt5ytf xz62fqu x16ldp7u\"></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"x1pi30zi x1swvt13\">\r\n<div class=\"x1ni5s2d\">\r\n<div class=\"x11i5rnm xat24cr x1mh8g0r x1vvkbs xtlvy1s\" style=\"text-align: center;\"></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">\r\n<div dir=\"ltr\">Come join us for a night of shared creativity!</div>\r\n<div dir=\"ltr\"></div>\r\n<div dir=\"ltr\">We welcome: all musical genres / poetry and spoken word / performers and listeners / pros and beginners / regulars and first-timers. No competition!</div>\r\n<div dir=\"ltr\"></div>\r\n<div dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Sign-up: 20.00 / start: 20.30 </strong></div>\r\n<div dir=\"ltr\"></div>\r\n<div dir=\"ltr\">Pre-sign-up possible here (limited slots!): link coming soon!</div>\r\n<div dir=\"ltr\"></div>\r\n<div dir=\"ltr\">Two songs or max. 10 mins per artist.</div>\r\n<div dir=\"ltr\"></div>\r\n<div dir=\"ltr\">We have: 2x vocal mic, 1x instrument mic, 1x electric piano, 2x jack cable/input, 1x input/cable for phone or laptop. Inform host at sign-up what you need.</div>\r\n<div dir=\"ltr\"></div>\r\n<div dir=\"ltr\">Follow us: <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/openmicljfox/\">https://www.instagram.com/openmicljfox/</a></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h3 dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align: center;\">M Love</h3>\r\n<div dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align: center;\">DJ-Set / Berlin</div>\r\n<div dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align: center;\">\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">M Love is a DJ and producer based in Berlin, releasing music on labels such as Relish and Play Pal. Drawing on post punk and Krautrock inspired motorik grooves, his eclectic sets blend indie dance with leftfield electronic music and psychedelia. As a  multi instrumentalist, he's also a member of the Berlin based bands Moriah Plaza and Cherry Bandora.</span>\r\n\r\n<a href=\"https://soundcloud.com/1mlove1?fbclid=IwAR3nnFhc1Q0GsvIJyDw-l47GJTsynwB0GCZ956R61ojDke7-DRjuzICmRwk\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">https://soundcloud.com/1mlove1</span></a>\r\n\r\n<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/1m_love1/\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">https://www.instagram.com/1m_love1/</span></a>\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-6154\" src=\"https://madameclaude.de/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/7456577347c01ad4-madameclaude-700x692.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"700\" height=\"692\" />\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-6153\" src=\"https://madameclaude.de/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/61657734753e104-madameclaude-583x700.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"583\" height=\"700\" />\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<div dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align: center;\"></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>",
