            "event_card_title": "SAM THERAPY + Jonathan Bergen + DJ Lichene",
            "event_description": "<h3>SAM THERAPY</h3>\r\nQueer Noise, Industrial, Power Electronics / Hannover Untergrund\r\n\r\nsam therapy. the name says it all: noise is a form of therapy – no prescription needed, only distortion pedals.\r\n\r\npersonal confession meets industrial coldness.\r\n\r\ntheir introspective lyrics are sometimes screamed, sometimes moaned.\r\n\r\nthrough synthesized chaos, they are trying to find a language for the struggle with depression, sickness, near-death experiences, and gender dysphoria.\r\n\r\n<a href=\"https://samtherapy.bandcamp.com\">https://samtherapy.bandcamp.com</a>\r\n\r\n<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/sonicbrutalism\">https://www.instagram.com/sonicbrutalism</a>\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-16039\" src=\"https://madameclaude.de/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/1146a4d632065f34-madameclaude-700x394.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"700\" height=\"394\" />\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-16038\" src=\"https://madameclaude.de/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/1366a4d62f07aaa1-madameclaude-502x700.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"502\" height=\"700\" />\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-16040\" src=\"https://madameclaude.de/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/1586a4d6341c0fe9-madameclaude-700x393.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"700\" height=\"393\" />\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-16041\" src=\"https://madameclaude.de/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/2316a4d636d883dc-madameclaude-700x691.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"700\" height=\"691\" />\r\n<h3>Jonathan Bergen</h3>\r\nCut Up Noise / Berlin\r\n\r\nJonathan Bergen, an interdisciplinary artist based in Berlin, is renowned for their explorations in ambient, noise, and cut-up sound performance.\r\n\r\nThey create immersive sonic environments transforming sound fragments into unpredictable compositions that blur the line between structure and chaos.\r\n\r\nEach work is a unique act of sonic deconstruction.\r\n\r\n<a href=\"https://bio.site/jonathanbergen\">https://bio.site/jonathanbergen</a>\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://Instagram.com/bergen.jonathan\">Instagram.com/bergen.jonathan</a>\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-16042\" src=\"https://madameclaude.de/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/3906a4d6434ddb31-madameclaude-525x700.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"525\" height=\"700\" />   <img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-16043\" src=\"https://madameclaude.de/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/446a4d643955d0f-madameclaude-527x700.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"527\" height=\"700\" />\r\n<h3>DJ Lichene</h3>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">DJ-Set / Berlin</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Drone / Ambient / Ritualist</span>\r\n\r\n<a href=\"https://m.mixcloud.com/licia-lithium/\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">https://m.mixcloud.com/licia-lithium/</span></a>\r\n\r\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/licia.elle\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">https://www.facebook.com/licia.elle</span></a>\r\n\r\n<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/licia_lithium_lichene/\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">https://www.instagram.com/licia_lithium_lichene/</span></a>\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-6139\" src=\"https://madameclaude.de/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/104657733d571115-madameclaude-scaled-700x525.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"700\" height=\"525\" />\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-8822\" src=\"https://madameclaude.de/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/7966676acdc883ae-madameclaude-700x700.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"700\" height=\"700\" />",
