            "event_description": "<strong>SCREENING SESSION - SHORTIES\r\n</strong><strong>Madame Claude´s original short film picks</strong>\r\n\r\nFilm lovers, creators, critics, makers, actors, watchers and breathers-\r\n\r\nWe can’t wait to welcome you and to hopefully build a little community to celebrate collaboration, friendship, and cinema.\r\n\r\nSubmissions taken via email: film.submissions.madameclaude@gmail.com\r\n\r\nOpen call details:\r\nAll forms, styles, genres, languages, fingernails and cakes welcome. Just please note the following:\r\n- An approximate duration range between 05:13-11:27.\r\n- Theoretically speaking we will not be accepting music videos. However, we invite you to dare to be an exception.\r\n<h3><img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-9988\" src=\"https://madameclaude.de/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/91266e84cb45dca6-madameclaude-700x648.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"700\" height=\"648\" /></h3>\r\n<h3>Avangelic (DJ-Set)</h3>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Based between the living and the departed </span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Dark blending of melodic bass, progressive trance, melodic techno, progressive house, and cinematic emotion.</span>\r\n\r\n<a href=\"https://open.spotify.com/artist/06giUxnJQvrZH9nyQqqN8T?si=31d8132abf154908\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">https://open.spotify.com/artist/06giUxnJQvrZH9nyQqqN8T?si=31d8132abf154908</span></a>\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://instagram.com/avengelicsounds\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">instagram.com/avengelicsounds</span></a>\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://tiktok.com/@avengelicsounds\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">tiktok.com/@avengelicsounds</span></a>\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-15470\" src=\"https://madameclaude.de/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/88269c6f0ed1db15-madameclaude-700x700.jpeg\" alt=\"\" width=\"700\" height=\"700\" />",
            "event_day_name": "Other"
        }
