            "event_description": "<h5 style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>Before we lock the doors for the summer, we’re handing the keys to the people who keep this place alive. </strong></h5>\r\n<h5 style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>Join us for a special showcase featuring our incredible roster of resident DJs and musicians. </strong></h5>\r\n<h5 style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>We’ve challenged each artist to a 'sprint' set—bringing you their best in a back-to-back marathon.</strong></h5>\r\n<h5 style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>Let’s send the season out on a high note. </strong></h5>\r\n<img class=\"size-medium wp-image-15861 aligncenter\" src=\"https://madameclaude.de/wp-content/uploads/2026/05/9096a03460080f85-madameclaude-700x366.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"700\" height=\"366\" />\r\n<h5 style=\"text-align: center;\"></h5>",
