            "event_card_subtitle": "we.make.berlin",
            "event_card_title": "POP-UP MARKET",
            "event_description": "Tired of visiting regular Sunday Flohmarkts? we.make.berlin is a curated craft market series born from a desire to bridge the gap between high-level design and the raw, creative energy of Berlin. Founded by a designer and fashion buyer, the project focuses on product curation, moving away from mass-produced and second hand items to highlight the 'craft' in every object. We believe that a market is also a Berlin community hub where the story of the maker is as important as the piece itself. By choosing iconic venues we create an atmosphere where there is something new to discover at every point of the journey. In an ever growing digital world, these events bring us into the tangible.\r\n\r\nFor our Madame Claude edition, we have hand-picked 15 Berlin-based makers. The lineup is a diverse mix of discipline and style\r\nYou will find : Contemporary Jewelry, Handthrown Ceramics, Upcycled Accessories, Illustrative Art, and Original Photography\r\n\r\nAs well as the market, you will also have the option to have some tooth gems applied, get a henna tattoo or get your tarot cards read.\r\n\r\nEvery vendor at this edition was selected not just for their skill, but for their unique creative voice. We are proud to host a group that values quality over quantity and community over competition.\r\n\r\n<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/we.make.berlin/\">https://www.instagram.com/we.make.berlin/</a>\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-15738\" src=\"https://madameclaude.de/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/29369e36b2798fee-madameclaude-525x700.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"525\" height=\"700\" />\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-15739\" src=\"https://madameclaude.de/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/56769e36b2e0564a-madameclaude-525x700.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"525\" height=\"700\" />\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-15740\" src=\"https://madameclaude.de/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/32569e36b3acd561-madameclaude-525x700.jpeg\" alt=\"\" width=\"525\" height=\"700\" />\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-15741\" src=\"https://madameclaude.de/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/48069e36b5209e21-madameclaude-700x467.jpeg\" alt=\"\" width=\"700\" height=\"467\" />\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-15742\" src=\"https://madameclaude.de/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/53969e36c122df94-madameclaude-467x700.jpeg\" alt=\"\" width=\"467\" height=\"700\" />\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-15743\" src=\"https://madameclaude.de/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/92369e36c1844230-madameclaude-467x700.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"467\" height=\"700\" />\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-15744\" src=\"https://madameclaude.de/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/5169e36c1f027eb-madameclaude-525x700.jpeg\" alt=\"\" width=\"525\" height=\"700\" />\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-15745\" src=\"https://madameclaude.de/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/72769e36c263f503-madameclaude-525x700.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"525\" height=\"700\" />\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-15715\" src=\"https://madameclaude.de/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/57469dd43ff2d3b0-madameclaude-560x700.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"560\" height=\"700\" />",
